### Post a message in a chatroom
POST {{base_url}}/message/chatrooms/{{chatroom_id}}/messages HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "content": "your_message"
}

###

### Retrieve all messages in a chatroom
GET {{base_url}}/message/chatrooms/{{chatroom_id}}/messages HTTP/1.1

###

### Delete a specific message
DELETE {{base_url}}/message/messages/{{message_id}} HTTP/1.1

###

### Retrieve messages in a chatroom after a specific timestamp
GET {{base_url}}/message/chatrooms/{{chatroom_id}}/messages/after/{{timestamp}} HTTP/1.1
